Package de.uni_mannheim.informatik.dws.melt.matching_data

This package contains the classes to support tracks and test cases. In MELT a track is a collection of one or more test cases. A test case is a concrete matching task. MELT is compatible with SEALS tracks. The MELT track repository infrastructure can also be found in this package.
